---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getDocBySlug } from '../../../data/navigation';

const doc = getDocBySlug('plugins');

if (!doc) {
	throw new Error('Plugins doc metadata is missing');
}
---

<Layout title={`${doc.title} | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档`} description={doc.summary} pathname={doc.path}>
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Build with Claude Code</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">Plugins 创建插件</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">{doc.summary}</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">官方 Plugins</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>插件就是把子代理、技能、配置打包成一个包，分享给别人或跨项目用。</p>
				<p>像浏览器插件，装上就能用，不用每次都重新配置。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">插件能打包啥</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-5 leading-8">
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">子代理</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">打包你养的小徒弟们，别人装上就能使唤。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">技能</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">打包你的绝活招式，分享给团队。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">MCP 服务器配置</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">打包外接设备的配置，一键安装。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">提示词模板</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">打包常用提示词，团队统一风格。</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">插件结构</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>插件是个目录，包含 <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">package.json</code> 和资源文件：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre>my-plugin/
├── package.json          # 插件元信息
├── agents/               # 子代理目录
│   ├── code-reviewer.md
│   └── test-writer.md
├── skills/               # 技能目录
│   └── api-conventions.md
└── mcp.json              # MCP 服务器配置</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">package.json 示例</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre><![CDATA[{
  "name": "@yourname/claude-code-review-plugin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "代码审查插件包",
  "claudeCode": {
    "agents": ["./agents/*.md"],
    "skills": ["./skills/*.md"],
    "mcp": "./mcp.json"
  }
}]]></pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">安装插件</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				<p><strong>从 npm 安装</strong> — <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">claude plugins install @yourname/claude-code-review-plugin</code></p>
				<p><strong>本地安装</strong> — <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">claude plugins install ./path/to/plugin</code></p>
				<p><strong>从 Git 安装</strong> — <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">claude plugins install github:user/repo</code></p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">最后一句土话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>插件就是把你的配置打包成"工具箱"，分享给别人或跨项目用。用好了，团队效率翻倍。</p>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">建议从打包自己的常用配置开始，慢慢完善成插件。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
